{"tid":629960,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"普通私樓係獨仔，定新私樓但有五兄弟姊妹？","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T03:50:27.000Z","uid":84579,"like":73,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8eb3becafb5041959f3d8c554e7b11675796999","tid":629960,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"普通私樓，但屋企唔算有錢，樣樣野都要慳，一出嚟做嘢要比一半家用，但會有一間你自己嘅房，一般供書教學都唔成問題<br />\n定係屋企有錢d,層樓新又大啲，每個月有好多零用錢俾你洗，供你去外國讀書都冇問題，但都未至於可以俾到幾兄弟姊妹每人一間獨立嘅房<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獨生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錢最重要"},{"pid":"5f574e21cc19998da9652dee30d9a510d6f04433","tid":629960,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9798aa7855eaf10e0f9407118321a621e435e83e","tid":629960,"uid":84579,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"講下原因啦<br />\n我自己本身係獨仔，生活free好多，話帶條女返嚟瞓就帶，閂埋房門就扑得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成世人用嘅嘢都係最新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但聽到啲fd講話要同兄弟share,帶咗條女返屋企先發現細佬喺度唔扑得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到都覺得慘"},{"pid":"4ccfb8f22d4649566093797bc2bdcff956cded9d","tid":629960,"uid":84579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cb9d2b4d17fe09c890c51c9e3e068e731f48fd","tid":629960,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062a788d9e733a79bb38cdfbca4bfba31db10311","tid":629960,"uid":74858,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"可以有好多零用去到外國讀書都冇房<img src=\"/